<br>
But I understand your point.  Yes, if you want to run a newly introduced quest in the future, you won't be able to (if it starts by killing something that is lower than your current level allows).  No two ways around that... it's going to be a fact of life on this server.<br>
<br>
However, what is the alternative?  Remove TLC altogether?  The cure would be worse than the symptom.  And while the complaints outnumber the defenders on this board (or so it would appear) I think this is more because people who are satisfied don't put time into rants outlining the fact.  I think the majority of players on this server are like myself:  it makes us work harder, but doesn't make it impossible. <p>Denoi Fishwhiskers<BR>
